  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13108975/voss_norway_off-piste_skiing_2.jpg" alt="NorwayHero" data-udi="umb://media/9d3c1b1daec3413380b1842b8cb91f7b" /></p>
<h2>Best ski areas in Norway</h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e}" title="Norway">Norway</a> is certainly renowned for its snow covered landscapes during the winter season and is the perfect place to enjoy some Nordic <a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">skiing</a>. A Scandinavian country that embraces the great outdoors, explore all that the Norwegian slopes have to offer on your next ski trip.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b}" title="Narvik" class="c-btn">Narvik</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/7a78ef87c3db4761821d6d628e884f3b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a78ef87c3db4761821d6d628e884f3b}" title="Myrkdalen" class="c-btn">Myrkdalen</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857}" title="Voss" class="c-btn">Voss</a></p>
<h2>Best Norwegian ski areas</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3>Western Norway ski area - best for all ski abilities &amp; snowboarders</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13108965/voss_norway_snowboarding_2.jpg" alt="WesternNorway" data-udi="umb://media/9b5cb733037f49aeb56549420721a2d0" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ski area</strong> - Western Norway</li>
<li><strong>Resorts</strong> - <a data-udi="umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857}" title="Voss">Voss</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/7a78ef87c3db4761821d6d628e884f3b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a78ef87c3db4761821d6d628e884f3b}" title="Myrkdalen">Myrkdalen</a></li>
</ul>
<h4>Voss highlights: </h4>
<ul>
<li><strong>KM of slopes</strong> - 40km</li>
<li><strong>Off-piste</strong> - Yes</li>
<li><strong>Crosscountry</strong> - Yes</li>
<li><strong>Snowparks</strong> - 1</li>
</ul>
<h4>Myrkdalen highlights: </h4>
<ul>
<li><strong>KM of slopes</strong> - 32km</li>
<li><strong>Off-piste</strong> - Yes</li>
<li><strong>Crosscountry</strong> - No</li>
<li><strong>Snowparks</strong> - 1</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Inghams top tip - Take a day trip to the city of Bergen and embrace the Nordic way of living with lots of museums that delve into the way of life here. </em></p>
<h4>The area:</h4>
<p>The western side of Norway is a very family originated part of the country, ideal for a <a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">family skiing trip</a>.</p>
<p>They enjoy lots of local traditions throughout the year, but during the winter months and especially the lead up to <a data-udi="umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee}" title="Christmas Skiing">Christmas</a>, family baking is a much loved weekend hobby. All the extended family will join together to make sweet treats for the festive period. Ideal for tourists as you will often find some of these yummy sweet treats in the resorts <a data-udi="umb://document/7f3fadf5a9e14a7a9340ea2ab9cb1934" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f3fadf5a9e14a7a9340ea2ab9cb1934}" title="Best ski resort Christmas markets">Christmas markets</a>.</p>
<h4>The skiing:</h4>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7020b15bdbb4234b4cdfe8de5c31857}" title="Voss">Voss</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/7a78ef87c3db4761821d6d628e884f3b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a78ef87c3db4761821d6d628e884f3b}" title="Myrkdalen">Myrkdalen</a> are the larger of the Norway resorts and offer the most out of the spaces here, with off-piste and night-skiing options. </p>
<p>If you are travelling as a family with younger children, then Myrkdalen is ideal - with a dedicated children's area and children's park to cater for them, plus an excellent ski-school with English speaking instructors.</p>
<p>Voss however is perfect for those who are a bit more adventurous on the slopes, showcasing a giant slalom course and a SuperG course. Voss also caters for those with a passion for <a data-udi="umb://document/9dc6a6fe70fb4ec4ab3e1eec8316020d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dc6a6fe70fb4ec4ab3e1eec8316020d}" title="Cross Country Ski Holidays">crosscountry</a>, showcasing 18km of trails through the stunning scenery that surrounds this resort.</p>
<h4>The resorts:</h4>
<p>The resorts of Voss and Myrkdalen offer everything you would expect from lively Norwegian towns - with plenty of cafes and restaurants to visit, plus some great apres-ski bars to celebrate your ski wins.</p>
<p>The resort of Voss is only 100km from the city of Bergen, great for a day out - it's worth travelling up the unique Ulriken cable car for an amazing view of the city and port. <br />Myrkdalen resort is more closely knit so you will find a lot of <a data-udi="umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41babb0d819449c09ee95e90e669265b}" title="Ski In Ski Out Holidays">ski-in ski-out</a> accommodation here and all the local amenities just a stones throw away.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/27de9e14dffb499081067a1e98ad813e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/27de9e14dffb499081067a1e98ad813e}" title="Norway" class="c-btn">View Norway deals</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3>Northern Norway ski area - best for beginners &amp; advanced</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13108939/narvik_northern_norway_off_piste_skiing.jpg" alt="NorthernNorway" data-udi="umb://media/c4aa2d49f2e94af3b3742e1172147098" /></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ski area</strong> - Western Norway</li>
<li><strong>Resorts</strong> - <a data-udi="umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b}" title="Narvik">Narvik</a></li>
</ul>
<h4>Narvik highlights: </h4>
<ul>
<li><strong>KM of slopes</strong> - 10km</li>
<li><strong>Off-piste</strong> - Yes</li>
<li><strong>Crosscountry</strong> - Yes</li>
<li><strong>Snowparks</strong> - 0<br /><br /></li>
</ul>
<p><em>Inghams top tip - Being located within the Arctic Circle, the chance of spotting the Northern Lights here are heightened so keep a look out. </em></p>
<h4>The area:</h4>
<p>The area of Northern Norway is quite influenced by Denmark. Northern Norway is a stunning place to visit during the ski season - within the arctic circle, you will see large glistening frozen lakes and the glow of the famous <a data-udi="umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995}" title="Northern Lights">Northern Lights</a>.</p>
<p>Make the most of your stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e}" title="Norway">Norway</a> and spend some time in the many saunas, a favourite past-time of the Nordic population. Most accommodation and all spas will have saunas on offer, the ideal way to relax after spending the day on the slopes. A great local favourite breakfast or sweet to try are the variety of sweet bread buns (known as School Bread).</p>
<h4>The skiing:</h4>
<p>Though <a data-udi="umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b}" title="Narvik">Narvik</a> is a smaller resort, it is a more rounded resort - offering a balance of slopes for every level of skiing. From great practice areas to cruisy blues, <a data-udi="umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1}" title="Ski Holidays for Beginners">beginners</a> will feel comfortable here to build up their skills.</p>
<p>For the <a data-udi="umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb}" title="Skiing for Advanced">advanced</a> skiers among you, there are some great challenging trails. Scandinavia's biggest vertical drops, a thrilling diamond-black run and some adventurous off-piste options can all be found.</p>
<h4>The resort:</h4>
<p>The resort of Narvik is located around one of Norway's most extensive and important harbours of the north, offering a great outlook on the arctic circle location.</p>
<p>The Norwegians consider the resort of Narvik their home for winter sports so you will often see locals at this resort for the weekends. Rich in history and nature, this resort offers more than your standard ski escape and a week here will be thoroughly enjoyed.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/336a323374f046cfa0591948e538170e}" title="Norway" class="c-btn">View Norway</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Skiing in Europe</h2>
<p>Have a look at some other amazing ski destinations for your next skiing holiday:</p>
